<SceneText>
  <FriendlyName>Chapter 2 (Lloyd) - End</FriendlyName>
  <Speakers>
    <Section>Speaker</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>クロエ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Chloe</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>15</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>セネル</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Senel</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>14</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ロイド</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Lloyd</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>10</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ゼロス</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Zelos</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>11</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>すまなかった。
まさか私の知人に非があったとは……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm sorry for that. I would never have guessed
an acquaintance of mine was the one at fault.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>15</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>まったく。
相変わらずクロエはそそっかしいな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Geez. As careless as ever, Chloe...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>14</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>返す言葉もない</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>There's nothing I can really say to that.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>15</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>気にする事ないって。
ちゃんと説明しなかった
ゼロスも悪いんだからさ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Don't worry about it. It was Zelos' bad too
that he didn't even bother to explain
anything properly.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>10</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>おいおい、ロイドくん。
どっちの味方よ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Hey now, Lloyd-kun, who's side are you on?</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>11</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そんなの決まってるだろ
俺は正直者の味方なんだよ</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Isn't that obvious? I'm on the side of honest folk.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>10</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>トホホ。
それって最高の嫌みね……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oof. That's the most cutting
remark you could've made...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>11</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
